{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"交叉轴","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Cross_Axis","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>弹性容器 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Flexbox\">flexbox</a> 的交叉轴和主轴 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Main_Axis\">main axis</a> 垂直，因此如果弹性方向是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-direction\"><code>flex-direction</code></a> 行 <code>row</code> 或者反向行 <code>row-reverse</code> ，那么交叉轴就是从上至下地垂直走向的。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cross_Axis/basics3.png\" alt=\"The cross axis runs down the column\" width=\"666\" height=\"125\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>如果你的主轴是列 <code>column</code> 或者反向列 <code>column-reverse</code> ，那么交叉轴就是水平走向的。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Cross_Axis/basics4.png\" alt=\"The cross axis runs along the row.\" width=\"523\" height=\"244\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>要在交叉轴上对齐，是通过弹性容器的 <code>align-items</code> 属性来控制的，或者通过弹性元素的 <code>align-self</code> 属性来单独决定的对齐方式。在多行弹性容器中，交叉轴上有多余控件的话，你还可以用 <code>align-content</code> 来控制行的间距。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"学习更多","title":"学习更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性参考","title":"属性参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-content\"><code>align-content</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-items\"><code>align-items</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/align-self\"><code>align-self</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-wrap\"><code>flex-wrap</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex-direction\"><code>flex-direction</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/flex\"><code>flex</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"拓展阅读","title":"拓展阅读","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>CSS 弹性容器指南：<em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Flexbox\">Basic Conc